  "texts": [
    "The termination of employees was interpreted as node label as outcome variable.",
    "The article does not consider termination as a node label influenced by a spreading mechanism.",
    "The literature discusses the network pattern related to turnovers and usually finds that those with low centrality are more likely to quit [16] [17] [18], which was further investigated 19.",
    "Hypotheses are frequently used as a starting point when investigating the background factors of the outcome variable.",
    "In our data-driven approach, we did not have presumptions, but we sought the strongest predictors and used an explainable machine learning approach."
